317
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:58,530
Tell me!

318
00:22:58,530 --> 00:23:01,190
I like you! That has nothing to do with Ingpha!

319
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:14,650
I like you, Ken.

320
00:23:17,380 --> 00:23:19,120
I've been in love with you since the day I saved you.

321
00:23:22,550 --> 00:23:23,830
