339
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:25,950
Are you going out?

340
00:25:29,740 --> 00:25:30,470
Are you going out with Lue?

341
00:25:34,140 --> 00:25:34,980
No.

342
00:25:36,570 --> 00:25:37,320
Where is your phone?

343
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:44,310
Where is your phone?

344
00:25:45,020 --> 00:25:45,800
Ken!

345
00:25:46,870 --> 00:25:47,840
You did it again!

346
00:25:55,850 --> 00:26:00,540
