352
00:27:49,990 --> 00:27:50,530
Yes.

353
00:27:53,350 --> 00:27:54,640
Nice to meet you.

354
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:07,260
I am the mayor here.

355
00:28:07,490 --> 00:28:09,770
Feel free to let me know if you need anything.

356
00:28:10,930 --> 00:28:13,980
How is your timber mill? You export the wood to the international market.

357
00:28:25,600 --> 00:28:26,580
What's wrong?

358
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:29,900
Sorry.

359
00:28:31,330 --> 00:28:32,450
I spaced out.

360
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,630
I forgot that Thai people

361
00:28:35,250 --> 00:28:36,390
don't grip so hard when shaking hands.

362
00:28:39,520 --> 00:28:40,020
Yes.

363
00:28:40,990 --> 00:28:42,270
Oh.

364
00:28:43,900 --> 00:28:46,400
The wood here is great. Do you know that?

365
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,230
There are plenty of rare wood

366
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:49,720
in this place.

367
00:28:50,950 --> 00:28:52,700
If you need or want anything,

368
00:28:53,260 --> 00:28:55,220
