369
00:28:55,690 --> 00:28:57,440
Everyone here knows me.

370
00:29:00,950 --> 00:29:01,430
Take this.

371
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:03,820
It's a pleasure to meet you.

372
00:29:07,930 --> 00:29:09,360
I'll certainly need some help from you

373
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:10,980
and Miss Ae.

374
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,010
Thank you.

375
00:29:44,480 --> 00:29:44,930
Honey?

376
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:46,560
Honey.

377
00:29:49,150 --> 00:29:50,770
-Thank you.
-Thanks.

378
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:53,710
You should eat up.

379
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:55,170
You should eat up.

380
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:56,780
You're so skinny. You should put up some weight.

381
00:29:59,460 --> 00:30:00,440
I won't take your food.

382
00:30:00,800 --> 00:30:01,420
You won't need to.

383
00:30:01,770 --> 00:30:02,680
Sweetheart.

384
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:03,620
Sweetheart.

385
00:30:03,620 --> 00:30:04,370
Sweetheart.

386
00:30:05,810 --> 00:30:06,840
Hey, Ken.

387
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:08,030
Oh.

388
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,110
-Dr. Chayon.
-Ken.

389
00:30:10,720 --> 00:30:11,300
Well?

390
00:30:11,780 --> 00:30:12,780
Are you feeling okay?

391
00:30:13,260 --> 00:30:13,480
Yeah.

392
00:30:14,100 --> 00:30:14,990
How are you?

393
00:30:14,990 --> 00:30:16,540
We haven't met in two years.

394
00:30:17,370 --> 00:30:18,430
I was worried about you.

395
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:19,570
Take a seat.

396
00:30:21,630 --> 00:30:22,230
Come on.

397
00:30:22,390 --> 00:30:23,590
Sit here.

398
00:30:27,650 --> 00:30:30,420
He really wanted to give you a surprise.

399
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:33,560
He came all the way here from Seoul.

400
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:34,320
Yeah.

401
00:30:35,780 --> 00:30:36,530
That's nice.

402
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:39,670
The two doctors can keep an eye on him.

403
00:30:39,890 --> 00:30:42,090
He's been a bit blur lately.

404
00:30:42,940 --> 00:30:44,630
He keeps spacing out.

405
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:47,440
Do you still have your phone?

406
00:30:48,740 --> 00:30:49,640
It's right here.

407
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:51,290
Yeah.

408
00:30:53,170 --> 00:30:53,520
By the way,

409
00:30:54,580 --> 00:30:55,210
do you

410
