427
00:31:55,710 --> 00:31:56,670
Yeah.

428
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,570
That's enough, doctor.

429
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:00,650
What's enough?

430
00:32:01,590 --> 00:32:02,760
What is it, Mr. Lue?

431
00:32:03,360 --> 00:32:04,340
Fine, I'll ask Ken.

432
00:32:05,110 --> 00:32:05,970
What do you think?

433
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:08,010
How did you meet and become so close?

434
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:14,050
I don't know what to say.

435
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:19,930
Come on, Ken. Wouldn't you let me in on this?

436
00:32:20,290 --> 00:32:21,200
Please?

437
00:32:23,170 --> 00:32:25,120
How did you meet? I'm so curious.

438
00:32:27,360 --> 00:32:28,130
Tell her.

439
00:32:28,330 --> 00:32:29,140
Yeah.

440
00:32:29,920 --> 00:32:31,130
That's all.

441
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:32,390
Enough, doctor.

442
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:44,530
Mr. Lue.

443
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,130
Grab my arm.

444
00:36:49,500 --> 00:36:50,070
Wow.

445
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:52,470
This shop is beautiful.

446
00:36:52,710 --> 00:36:53,280
Yeah.

447
00:36:53,850 --> 00:36:55,690
