00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,990
-Hello.
-Hello.

454
00:37:04,990 --> 00:37:05,550
Welcome in.

455
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:06,640
Okay.

456
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:11,810
Wow...

457
00:37:20,690 --> 00:37:24,450
