458
00:37:24,930 --> 00:37:25,640
Yeah.

459
00:37:26,130 --> 00:37:27,250
It looks delicious.

460
00:37:28,040 --> 00:37:28,850
Eat up.

461
00:37:28,850 --> 00:37:31,040
By the way, where is the menu for dessert?

462
00:37:31,390 --> 00:37:33,630
Be patient, Sai. Finish your meal first.

463
00:37:34,810 --> 00:37:38,080
The dessert is not the main course. So, it's okay to finish either one of them first.

464
00:37:38,080 --> 00:37:40,980
Don't worry. I'll let you order the dessert, okay?

465
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:43,020
Okay. Good.

466
00:37:45,430 --> 00:37:47,290
I want pork jerky

467
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:50,270
and traditional crispy noodles.

468
00:37:53,520 --> 00:37:54,870
Let me repeat your order.

469
00:37:54,870 --> 00:37:57,130
Pork jerky and traditional crispy noodles, right?

470
00:37:57,130 --> 00:37:57,810
Yes.

471
00:37:58,100 --> 00:37:58,990
That's 160 phat.

472
00:38:00,930 --> 00:38:02,410
I need to use the restroom.

473
00:38:02,700 --> 00:38:03,370
Sure.

474
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:07,510
This looks delicious too. It's beef.

475
00:38:07,820 --> 00:38:09,610
-It's a signature dish here.

476
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:11,640
It's prawn, right?

477
00:39:29,520 --> 00:39:30,270
Hahaha!

478
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:47,620
Nok!

479
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:48,670
It's me!

480
00:40:01,240 --> 00:40:02,390
So long!

481
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:10,310
Come and get me!

482
00:40:16,550 --> 00:40:18,330
Don't stop! I like the music!

483
00:40:21,990 --> 00:40:22,660
What now?

484
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:18,010
Get out of my sight!

485
00:41:21,840 --> 00:41:22,680
Hey!

486
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:18,310
He wants to see you.

487
00:42:21,140 --> 00:42:22,150
Is something the matter?

488
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:28,140
