507
00:44:56,750 --> 00:44:58,820
He's Ken's friend. I mentioned him.

508
00:44:59,700 --> 00:45:00,860
This is Officer Don.

509
00:45:01,500 --> 00:45:03,460
Nice to meet you, Officer Don.

510
00:45:03,680 --> 00:45:04,460
Nice to meet you too.

511
00:45:04,690 --> 00:45:05,220
Mr. Lue.

512
00:45:07,720 --> 00:45:09,790
I'll give you one last chance.

513
00:45:10,650 --> 00:45:11,270
Is that clear?

514
00:45:12,430 --> 00:45:13,770
Hahaha!

515
00:45:14,190 --> 00:45:15,960
Your order has been carried out and completed.

516
00:45:16,510 --> 00:45:18,270
[I pity Ken.]

517
00:45:18,270 --> 00:45:21,210
[His lover died. Now, he's being hunted.]

518
00:45:21,210 --> 00:45:24,160
[If Din were alive, he might be able to protect him.]

519
00:45:25,830 --> 00:45:28,800
Din is not dead yet! What you say is impossible!

520
00:45:28,930 --> 00:45:29,730
